    <title>堆分配器的设计与实现</title>
    <link href="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/"/>
    <url>/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="堆分配器的设计与实现"><a href="#堆分配器的设计与实现" class="headerlink" title="堆分配器的设计与实现"></a>堆分配器的设计与实现</h1><h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>Linux环境高级编程</p><p>C语言</p><h2 id="一、需求分析"><a href="#一、需求分析" class="headerlink" title="一、需求分析"></a>一、需求分析</h2><h3 id="1-1-总体要求"><a href="#1-1-总体要求" class="headerlink" title="1.1 总体要求"></a>1.1 总体要求</h3><p>实现一个堆分配器，即实现内存分配和释放的功能</p><h3 id="1-2-基本要求"><a href="#1-2-基本要求" class="headerlink" title="1.2 基本要求"></a>1.2 基本要求</h3><p>实现的内存分配函数名为MyMalloc，内存释放函数名为MyFree，这两个函数原型同malloc和free；</p><p>使用mmap函数从内核分配整个堆空间，而MyMalloc和MyFree管理该空间；</p><p>考虑内存碎片问题</p><p>要考虑并发性问题，即多个线程同时分配和释放内存的场景</p><h2 id="二、总体设计"><a href="#二、总体设计" class="headerlink" title="二、总体设计"></a>二、总体设计</h2><h3 id="2-1-总体设计概述"><a href="#2-1-总体设计概述" class="headerlink" title="2.1 总体设计概述"></a>2.1 总体设计概述</h3><p>接口层向外提供MyMalloc（）（内存申请）以及MyFree()，技术实现主要由内存分配，内存释放，内存碎片管理以及多线程并发管理组成，最下层调用了mmap()函数分配堆空间，程序流程图以及架构如下所示</p>  <img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/1-16517148912342.png" class="" width="1"><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/2-16517148912331.png" class="" width="2"><h3 id="2-2-具体模块设计"><a href="#2-2-具体模块设计" class="headerlink" title="2.2 具体模块设计"></a>2.2 具体模块设计</h3><h4 id="2-2-1-数据结构"><a href="#2-2-1-数据结构" class="headerlink" title="2.2.1 数据结构"></a>2.2.1 数据结构</h4><p>堆的管理涉及到两个数据结构，堆头(heap_header)以及内存块头(block_header)。</p><p><strong>堆头 heap_header</strong></p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-keyword">typedef</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title">heap_header</span>&#123;</span>  <br><span class="hljs-number">2.</span>    block_header* pre_free_block;  <br><span class="hljs-number">3.</span>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> heap_size;  <br><span class="hljs-number">4.</span>&#125;heap_header;  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结构体中包括pre_free_block和heap_size两个数据成员。pre_heap_break为当前第一个空闲内存块（本设计内存块分配策略为循环适应法），heap_size为堆的大小（包括堆头）。</p><p><strong>内存块头</strong></p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C"><span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-keyword">typedef</span> <span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title">block_header</span>&#123;</span>  <br><span class="hljs-number">2.</span>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> block_size;  <br><span class="hljs-number">3.</span>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> block_flag;  <br><span class="hljs-number">4.</span>&#125;block_header; <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结构体中包括block_size和block_flag两个数据成员。block_size为内存块的大小，block_flag为当前内存块是否空闲，0为空闲，1为已分配。</p><p>总体情况如下：</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/3-16517148912343.png" class="" width="3"><h4 id="2-2-2-内存分配与释放设计"><a href="#2-2-2-内存分配与释放设计" class="headerlink" title="2.2.2 内存分配与释放设计"></a>2.2.2 内存分配与释放设计</h4><p>由内存块数据结构可知，本设计没有将堆空间分页，在申请内存空间时，仅需依次向下遍历，访问到一块符合要求的内存块，修改大小以及标志位，并将剩余的空闲空间建立新的内存块头，即循环首次适应算法，容易产生外部碎片。释放内存亦是如此，如下图所示，</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/4-16517148912344.png" class="" width="4"><h4 id="2-2-3-内存碎片整理设计"><a href="#2-2-3-内存碎片整理设计" class="headerlink" title="2.2.3 内存碎片整理设计"></a>2.2.3 内存碎片整理设计</h4><p>正如上图所示，释放完一块内存块时候，会出现外部碎片，明显存在4072大小的空闲空间，但是如果此时申请大于2072大小的内存空间时会失败，因此需要整理内存碎片。本设计选择在用户申请内存块之前整理内存碎片，如下图所示：</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/5-16517148912345.png" class="" width="5"><h2 id="三、详细设计与实现"><a href="#三、详细设计与实现" class="headerlink" title="三、详细设计与实现"></a>三、详细设计与实现</h2><h3 id="3-1-初始化堆-init-heap"><a href="#3-1-初始化堆-init-heap" class="headerlink" title="3.1 初始化堆 init_heap()"></a>3.1 初始化堆 init_heap()</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C"><span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-comment">//初始化堆,heap_begin_addr = (long long)init_heap();  </span><br><span class="hljs-number">2.</span>heap_header* <span class="hljs-title function_">init_heap</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span>&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">3.</span>    heap_header* heap = (heap_header*)mmap(<span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>, <span class="hljs-number">4096</span>, PROT_WRITE, MAP_PRIVATE | MAP_ANONYMOUS, <span class="hljs-number">-1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">0</span>);  <br><span class="hljs-number">4.</span>    heap-&gt;pre_free_block = (block_header*)((<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)heap + heap_header_size);  <br><span class="hljs-number">5.</span>    heap-&gt;heap_size = file_size;  <br><span class="hljs-number">6.</span>    first_block = heap-&gt;pre_free_block;  <br><span class="hljs-number">7.</span>    first_block-&gt;block_flag = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;  <br><span class="hljs-number">8.</span>    first_block-&gt;block_size = file_size - heap_header_size - block_header_size;  <br><span class="hljs-number">9.</span>    <span class="hljs-comment">//memset(heap + heap_header_size, 0, heap-&gt;heap_size);         </span><br><span class="hljs-number">10.</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (heap_header*)heap;  <br><span class="hljs-number">11.</span>&#125; <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用mmap()函数从内核分配整个堆空间，将返回的地址赋值给堆首地址。此时堆的大小为file_size – heap_header_size，第一块空闲内存块首地址为heap + heap_header_size，空闲块大小为file_size - heap_header_size - block_header_size，并将block_flag置为0。初始化堆的过程中同时将首个内存块地址记录，后续碎片整理以及其他模块中需要用到。</p><h3 id="3-2-内存碎片整理-defrag"><a href="#3-2-内存碎片整理-defrag" class="headerlink" title="3.2 内存碎片整理 defrag()"></a>3.2 内存碎片整理 defrag()</h3><p>内存碎片整理的时机有很多，如malloc之前整理碎片，free之后整理碎片等，本设计选择mallc之前，从当前内存块位置往下整理碎片。代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">defrag</span><span class="hljs-params">(block_header* current_block)</span>&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">2.</span>    block_header* next_block = get_next_block(current_block);     <br><span class="hljs-number">3.</span>  <br><span class="hljs-number">4.</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(current_block-&gt;block_flag == <span class="hljs-number">0</span> &amp;&amp; next_block-&gt;block_flag == <span class="hljs-number">0</span> &amp;&amp; next_block != first_block)&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">5.</span>        current_block-&gt;block_size += (block_header_size + next_block-&gt;block_size);  <br><span class="hljs-number">6.</span>        <span class="hljs-comment">//memset(current_block + block_header_size, 0, current_block-&gt;block_size);  </span><br><span class="hljs-number">7.</span>        next_block = get_next_block(current_block);  <br><span class="hljs-number">8.</span>    &#125;  <br><span class="hljs-number">9.</span>  <br><span class="hljs-number">10.</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;  <br><span class="hljs-number">11.</span>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接收参数为当前内存块头地址，首先通过get_next_block()（第4章）函数获取下一块内存块地址，如果下一块内存块没有循环到第一块内存块，且当前内存块与下一块内存块的block_flag均为0时，可将两内存块合并，当前内存块头地址不变，block_size为当前内存块大小加上下一块内存块大小再加上一个内存块头大小，即current_block-&gt;block_size +&#x3D; (block_header_size + next_block-&gt;block_size)，再通过get_next_block()获取下一块内存块地址，继续整理内存碎片。流程图如下：</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/6-16517148912346.png" class="" width="6"><h3 id="3-3-获取下一块内存块地址-get-next-block"><a href="#3-3-获取下一块内存块地址-get-next-block" class="headerlink" title="3.3 获取下一块内存块地址 get_next_block()"></a>3.3 获取下一块内存块地址 get_next_block()</h3><p>获取下一块内存块头的方式与数据结构有关，由图1可知，获取下一块内存块头仅需当前内存块头地址加上当前内存块大小以及一个内内存块头大小，即next_blocl &#x3D; current_block + current_block-&gt;block_size + block_header_size</p><p>,代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-comment">//获取下一个内存块地址   </span><br><span class="hljs-number">2.</span>block_header* <span class="hljs-title function_">get_next_block</span><span class="hljs-params">(block_header* current_block)</span>&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">3.</span>    heap_header* heap = heap_begin_addr;  <br><span class="hljs-number">4.</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> ((block_header*)((<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)current_block + current_block-&gt;block_size + block_header_size) &gt;= (block_header*)((<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)heap_begin_addr + heap-&gt;heap_size)) &#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">5.</span>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (block_header*)((<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)heap_begin_addr + heap_header_size);  <br><span class="hljs-number">6.</span>    &#125;  <br><span class="hljs-number">7.</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> &#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">8.</span>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (block_header*)((<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)current_block + current_block-&gt;block_size + block_header_size);  <br><span class="hljs-number">9.</span>    &#125;  <br><span class="hljs-number">10.</span>&#125;  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>过程中会将计算到的可能是下一块的地址与堆的最后地址（heap_begin_addr + heap_size）对比，如果此地址已经超过我们堆的地址，则此时循环到堆首，将第一个内存块头地址返回，否则返回计算出的下一个内存块头地址。</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/7-16517146665783.png" class="" width="7"><h3 id="3-4-内存分配-MyMalloc"><a href="#3-4-内存分配-MyMalloc" class="headerlink" title="3.4 内存分配 MyMalloc()"></a>3.4 内存分配 MyMalloc()</h3><p>代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-type">void</span>* <span class="hljs-title function_">MyMalloc</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> mem_size)</span>&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">2.</span>    heap_header* heap = heap_begin_addr;  <br><span class="hljs-number">3.</span>    block_header* origin_block = heap-&gt;pre_free_block;  <br><span class="hljs-number">4.</span>    block_header* current_block = origin_block;  <br><span class="hljs-number">5.</span>      <br><span class="hljs-number">6.</span>    pthread_mutex_lock(&amp;mutex);  <br><span class="hljs-number">7.</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">do</span>&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">8.</span>        defrag(current_block);  <br><span class="hljs-number">9.</span>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(current_block-&gt;block_size &gt;= mem_size &amp;&amp; current_block-&gt;block_flag == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">10.</span>            current_block-&gt;block_flag = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;  <br><span class="hljs-number">11.</span>            block_header* next_block = (block_header*)((<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)current_block + block_header_size + mem_size);  <br><span class="hljs-number">12.</span>            next_block-&gt;block_size = current_block-&gt;block_size - block_header_size - mem_size;  <br><span class="hljs-number">13.</span>            next_block-&gt;block_flag = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;  <br><span class="hljs-number">14.</span>            current_block-&gt;block_size = mem_size;              <br><span class="hljs-number">15.</span>            <span class="hljs-comment">//memset(current_block + block_header_size, 1, mem_size);  </span><br><span class="hljs-number">16.</span>            heap-&gt;pre_free_block = next_block;  <br><span class="hljs-number">17.</span>            <span class="hljs-type">size_t</span> return_addr = (<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)current_block + block_header_size;  <br><span class="hljs-number">18.</span>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (<span class="hljs-type">void</span>*)return_addr;  <br><span class="hljs-number">19.</span>        &#125;  <br><span class="hljs-number">20.</span>        current_block = get_next_block(current_block);        <br><span class="hljs-number">21.</span>    &#125;<span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(current_block != origin_block);  <br><span class="hljs-number">22.</span>    pthread_mutex_unlock(&amp;mutex);  <br><span class="hljs-number">23.</span>  <br><span class="hljs-number">24.</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>;  <br><span class="hljs-number">25.</span>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>何时分配内存块？当前的内存块头的block_flag &#x3D;&#x3D; 0，block_size &gt; mem_size(申请内存块大小)时，可将当前内存块分配；</p><p>如果可以分配，做些什么？将当前内存块的block_flag &#x3D; 1，表示已被分配，获取下一块内存块头地址，为next_block &#x3D; current_block + block_header_size + mem_size，计算当前与下一块内存块的大小，current_block-&gt;block_size &#x3D; mem_size，next_block-&gt;block_size &#x3D; current_block-&gt;block_size - block_header_size - mem_size，并将下一块内存块的block_flag &#x3D; 0，表示为空闲内存块；</p><p>如果不能分配，做些什么？通过get_next_block()函数获取下一块内存块，继续重复上算法；</p><p>什么时候终止（即所申请内存大小不能满足）？一开始我们初始化了一个origin_block用来存放分配时第一个访问的内存块，即pre_free_block，如果一直未能获取满足要求的内存块，一直通过get_next_block()获取下一块内存块直到循环到了最开始的内存块，此时表明堆中已没有满足要求的内存块，此时退出函数，return NULL，表示申请失败。</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/8-16517148912347.png" class="" width="8"><p>如上代码在测试过程中出现了段错误，分析之后问题如下图所示，</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/9-16517146959084.png" class="" width="9"><p>此时我们堆空间中存在一个4072大小的空闲块，如果这时我们直接申请一个4072内存大小内存块会出现什么情况？</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/10-16517148912348.png" class="" width="10"><p>如果创建下一个空闲块头时，如果剩余空间小于等于8，不创建即可，修改后代码如下，</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c"><span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-type">void</span>* <span class="hljs-title function_">MyMalloc</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> mem_size)</span>&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">2.</span>    heap_header* heap = heap_begin_addr;  <br><span class="hljs-number">3.</span>    block_header* origin_block = heap-&gt;pre_free_block;  <br><span class="hljs-number">4.</span>    block_header* current_block = origin_block;  <br><span class="hljs-number">5.</span>      <br><span class="hljs-number">6.</span>    pthread_mutex_lock(&amp;mutex);  <br><span class="hljs-number">7.</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">do</span>&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">8.</span>        defrag(current_block);  <br><span class="hljs-number">9.</span>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(current_block-&gt;block_size &gt;= mem_size &amp;&amp; current_block-&gt;block_flag == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">10.</span>            current_block-&gt;block_flag = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;  <br><span class="hljs-number">11.</span>            block_header* next_block;  <br><span class="hljs-number">12.</span>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(((<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)current_block + <span class="hljs-number">2</span>*block_header_size + mem_size) &lt;= ((<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)heap + heap-&gt;heap_size))&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">13.</span>                next_block = (block_header*)((<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)current_block + block_header_size + mem_size);  <br><span class="hljs-number">14.</span>                next_block-&gt;block_size = current_block-&gt;block_size - block_header_size - mem_size;  <br><span class="hljs-number">15.</span>                next_block-&gt;block_flag = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;  <br><span class="hljs-number">16.</span>            &#125;  <br><span class="hljs-number">17.</span>            <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>   <br><span class="hljs-number">18.</span>                next_block = first_block;  <br><span class="hljs-number">19.</span>            current_block-&gt;block_size = mem_size;              <br><span class="hljs-number">20.</span>            <span class="hljs-comment">//memset(current_block + block_header_size, 1, mem_size);  </span><br><span class="hljs-number">21.</span>            heap-&gt;pre_free_block = next_block;  <br><span class="hljs-number">22.</span>            <span class="hljs-type">size_t</span> return_addr = (<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span>)current_block + block_header_size;  <br><span class="hljs-number">23.</span>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (<span class="hljs-type">void</span>*)return_addr;  <br><span class="hljs-number">24.</span>        &#125;  <br><span class="hljs-number">25.</span>        current_block = get_next_block(current_block);        <br><span class="hljs-number">26.</span>    &#125;<span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(current_block != origin_block);  <br><span class="hljs-number">27.</span>    pthread_mutex_unlock(&amp;mutex);  <br><span class="hljs-number">28.</span>  <br><span class="hljs-number">29.</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-literal">NULL</span>;  <br><span class="hljs-number">30.</span>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-5-内存释放-MyFree"><a href="#3-5-内存释放-MyFree" class="headerlink" title="3.5 内存释放 MyFree()"></a>3.5 内存释放 MyFree()</h3><p>代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C"><span class="hljs-number">1.</span><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">MyFree</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">size_t</span> addr)</span>&#123;  <br><span class="hljs-number">2.</span>    block_header* current_block = (block_header*)(addr - block_header_size);  <br><span class="hljs-number">3.</span>      <br><span class="hljs-number">4.</span>    pthread_mutex_lock(&amp;mutex);  <br><span class="hljs-number">5.</span>    current_block-&gt;block_flag = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;  <br><span class="hljs-number">6.</span>    <span class="hljs-comment">//memset(addr, 1, current_block-&gt;block_size);  </span><br><span class="hljs-number">7.</span>    pthread_mutex_unlock(&amp;mutex);  <br><span class="hljs-number">8.</span>    <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;内存释放成功！\n\n&quot;</span>);  <br><span class="hljs-number">9.</span>  <br><span class="hljs-number">10.</span>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;  <br><span class="hljs-number">11.</span>&#125;  <br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>由于MyMalloc()函数返回的是内存块的数据部分地址（即current_block + block_header_size），则MyFree()时需将获得到的地址减去内存块头的大小，得到此内存块头的地址，即current_block &#x3D; addr - block_header_size，并且由于内存碎片整理是在分配时进行，此时仅需将当前内存块头block_flag &#x3D; 0即可。</p><h3 id="3-6-并发性问题"><a href="#3-6-并发性问题" class="headerlink" title="3.6 并发性问题"></a>3.6 并发性问题</h3><p>调用pthread.h库，利用pthread_mutex_lock()以及pthread_mutex_unlock()两个函数完成信号量的操作，即PV操作。</p><p>本设计中内存块资源为临界资源，因此考虑并发性问题（多个线程同时分配和释放内存的场景）就是考虑关于内存块这个临界资源的操作。本设计中涉及到内存块的操作的仅有defrag()，MyMalloc()，MyFree()三个模块，而且defrag()模块是在MyMalloc()模块内调用，故只需要将这两个模块进行的内存块操作夹在P操作和V操作之间即可，如下: </p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/11-16517148912349.png" class="" width="11"><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/12-165171489123410.png" class="" width="12"><h2 id="四、测试"><a href="#四、测试" class="headerlink" title="四、测试"></a>四、测试</h2><h3 id="4-1-测试环境"><a href="#4-1-测试环境" class="headerlink" title="4.1 测试环境"></a>4.1 测试环境</h3><p>测试环境如下图：</p><h3 id="4-2-测试用例及测试结果"><a href="#4-2-测试用例及测试结果" class="headerlink" title="4.2 测试用例及测试结果"></a>4.2 测试用例及测试结果</h3><h4 id="4-2-1-测试用例1"><a href="#4-2-1-测试用例1" class="headerlink" title="4.2.1 测试用例1"></a>4.2.1 测试用例1<img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/13-165171489123411.png" class="" width="13"></h4><p>mmap申请4096大小内存空间，利用MyMalloc连续申请1992、1992、72大小空间。</p><p>此用例最后申请72后，堆头，内存块头以及数据域之和大小刚好为4096，若最后申请73，结果应为申请失败。</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/14-16517147727325.png" class="" width="14"><p>测试结果</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/15-16517147891306.png" class="" width="15"><h4 id="4-2-2-测试用例2"><a href="#4-2-2-测试用例2" class="headerlink" title="4.2.2 测试用例2"></a>4.2.2 测试用例2</h4><p>连续申请4块1012大小堆空间，之后释放第2块，申请1块502大小对空间，最后申请2032大小堆空间。</p><p>堆空间变化应如下图所示，</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/16-165171489123412.png" class="" width="16"><p>测试结果:</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/17-16517148017137.png" class="" width="17"><h4 id="4-2-3-测试用例3"><a href="#4-2-3-测试用例3" class="headerlink" title="4.2.3 测试用例3"></a>4.2.3 测试用例3</h4><p>与用例1一样，首先申请1992，1992，72三块堆空间，此时堆空间正好被占满。之后释放第一块以及第三块内存块，测试内存碎片整理。如下图所示</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/18-165171489123413.png" class="" width="18"><p>释放第一以及最后一块内存块之后，虽然此时堆空间存在2080大小的空闲区域，但是可用的最大的还是只有2000，测试defrag()是否会错误整理内存碎片。</p><p>测试结果：</p><img src="/2022/05/05/%E5%A0%86%E5%88%86%E9%85%8D%E5%99%A8%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E4%B8%8E%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0/19-165171489123414.png" class="" width="19">]]></content>
    
    
