    <title>ret2libc2</title>
    <link href="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/"/>
    <url>/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="题目分析"><a class="header-anchor" href="#题目分析">¶</a>题目分析</h4><p>1、静态分析</p><p>​*当前程序为32位</p><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503104357552.png" class="" title="image-20220503104357552"><p>​*溢出点为gets()函数</p><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503104501626.png" class="" title="image-20220503104501626"><p>​*仅开启栈不可执行</p><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503104550249.png" class="" title="image-20220503104550249"><p>*存在system函数以及‘/bin/sh’字符串</p><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503104810343.png" class="" title="image-20220503104810343"><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503104853849.png" class="" title="image-20220503104853849"><p>2、动态分析</p><p>​*判断溢出点偏移位置</p><p>​a、随机生成长度200的字符串</p><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503105138710.png" class="" title="image-20220503105138710"><p>​b、利用gdb调试工具打开文件，并在main函数处设置断点</p><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503105410156.png" class="" title="image-20220503105410156"><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503105508276.png" class="" title="image-20220503105508276"><p>​c、输入字符串，获取溢出偏移量</p><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503105557402.png" class="" title="image-20220503105557402"><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503105648719.png" class="" title="image-20220503105648719"><p>3、攻击代码</p><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503105825397.png" class="" title="image-20220503105825397"><p>4、成功获得系统权限</p><img src="/2022/05/04/ret2libc2/image-20220503105926085.png" class="" title="image-20220503105926085">]]></content>
    
    
